General User Story Statement: As a Super Admin, I want to view consolidated metrics from all management systems on one dashboard, so that I can assess overall platform health and make informed decisions.
As a Super Admin, I want to search across all entities (For example: users, companies, projects, equipment , etc) from the main navigate bar
As a User, I want to switch between different user type perspectives (Company Owner, Manager, IT Admin, Investor), so that I can view different access levels across all management modules.
As a User, I want to search for users by name or ID and access their full profile details, so that I can quickly find and manage any user in the platform.
As a Super Admin, I want to manage user profiles throughout their lifecycle (creation, activation, verification, deactivation), so that I can maintain accurate user data and control platform access.
As a User, I want to manage user profiles throughout their lifecycle (creation, activation, verification, deactivation), so that I can maintain accurate user data and control platform access.
As an IT Admin, I want to assign and modify user roles within companies, so that team members have appropriate access levels for their responsibilities.
As a Super Admin, I want to configure the role-based permission matrix, so that I can control feature access across the platform and maintain security.
As a Company Owner, I want to create, edit, and manage custom roles within my organization, so that I can align platform permissions with my business structure.
As a user with different roles (Super Admin, Investor, Company Owner), I want to see analytics tailored to my role and responsibilities, so that I can make informed decisions
As a User (Company Owner, Manager) I want to create custom analytics dashboards with configurable widgets and metrics, so that I can track KPIs specific to my business needs.
As a Manager, I want to export analytics data and generate custom reports, so that I can share insights with stakeholders and support business decisions.
As a Super Admin, I want to manage all company profiles with their organizational structure, so that I can give them maintenance
As a Super Admin, I want to search and filter companies by various criteria (industry, size, status, location), so that I can quickly find and manage specific organizations.
As a Company Owner, I want to manage my team structure and department organization, so that I can organize my workforce and control access appropriately.
As a User, I want to view comprehensive audit logs of all user actions, so that I can ensure compliance, investigate issues, and maintain security.
As a User, I want to generate audit-ready reports, so that I can demonstrate regulatory adherence and support legal requirements.
As a Super Admin, I want to view and manage all projects across companies, so that I can monitor platform activity and resolve issues.
As a Manager, I want to create, assign, and track tasks within projects, so that I can ensure project deliverables are completed on time.
As a Manager, I want to review and manage the equipment that every project contains, so that I can ensure proper resource allocation and cost accuracy.
As a Manager, I want to review all project data including photos, reports, and estimates, so that I can ensure quality and completeness

As a Super Admin, I want to manage a comprehensive HVAC equipment reference database with pricing, specifications, and market information, so that the HVAC AI app can provide accurate cost estimates and equipment recommendations.
As a Super Admin, I want to manage equipment pricing information and cost analysis data, so that the HVAC AI system can provide accurate cost estimates for repairs and replacements.
As a Super Admin, I want to manage detailed technical specifications and industry standards for HVAC equipment, so that the AI system can make accurate compatibility and performance assessments.
As a Super Admin, I want to view all company subscriptions with plan type, status, and renewal dates, so that I can monitor billing health and prevent service interruptions.
As a Super Admin, I want to upgrade/downgrade company subscription plans, so that I can handle customer requests and optimize revenue.
As a Super Admin, I want to review and manage professional verification applications, so that I can maintain platform quality and enable verified professionals to access advanced features.
As an Investor, I want to view platform growth metrics, user engagement statistics, and business performance indicators, so that I can monitor the investment and make informed decisions.
